data.description: Exquisite 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home located in the highly sought-after Hitchcock Crossing neighborhood! Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a bright and inviting entryway adorned with a vaulted ceiling. To the left, a formal living area awaits, providing the perfect space to entertain guests or relax in style. Flowing seamlessly from the living room, the formal dining room boasts a statement light fixture, creating an elegant ambiance for unforgettable dinners and gatherings. The heart of this home lies in the beautifully appointed kitchen with ample cabinets for storage, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a tasteful tile backsplash. The central kitchen island not only provides additional workspace but also acts as a hub for family and friends to gather around. Connected to the kitchen is a spacious and comfortable living area, where a wood-burning stone fireplace stands as a stunning focal point, offering warmth and charm on cooler evenings. Upstairs, the generously sized bedrooms are flooded with natural light, creating inviting spaces for relaxation and rest. The Jack and Jill bathroom offers convenience and style, featuring a tub/shower combination and twin vanities, perfect for accommodating family members or guests. The expansive primary suite is an oasis of comfort and luxury, offering ample space for a sitting area, accompanied by a generously sized walk-in closet. The en suite bathroom boasts a double sink vanity, a soothing garden tub, and a separate tile shower. Transitioning to the outdoors, a spacious covered back porch invites you to enjoy the serene atmosphere of the large fenced backyard. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee or hosting an al fresco gathering, this outdoor space offers the perfect blend of privacy and relaxation. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this exceptional property your new home!
